		<title>狗狗搖尾巴代表開心？背後隱藏的「四種含義」飼主必須了解！ </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/08/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e6%90%96%e5%b0%be%e5%b7%b4%e4%bb%a3%e8%a1%a8%e9%96%8b%e5%bf%83%ef%bc%9f%e8%83%8c%e5%be%8c%e9%9a%b1%e8%97%8f%e7%9a%84%e3%80%8c%e5%9b%9b%e7%a8%ae%e5%90%ab%e7%be%a9%e3%80%8d%e9%a3%bc/</link>
		
